#

Slow Cooker Borscht

495 min
$12.99
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Comfort FoodSlow Cooker

Description

A hearty and comforting beet soup that simmers to perfection in your slow cooker, perfect for chilly nights.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 cups, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • potatoes: 2, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • bay leaves: 2
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
